Terrorists Commit 'Blasphemy,' Says Merkel - Worldnews.com

 Terrorists killing people in the name of god are committing “blasphemy,” German Chancellor Angela Merkel said, calling on Islamic leaders to clarify the relationship between their religion and the militants who claim to act in its name.

